reviewText: Disappointing it shows several women on the cover but at least one of them isn't even in the film, and some of the others were just reusing images from another film. It also looks like one character was just CGI from a previous film can you rate it less then 1 star? Please note I had no problem with the shipping, my problems lie in the film itself.  Look for "The Witches of Breastwich" or "The Breastford Wives" much higher quality films that feature Gloria Ann
We're very much a crazy society for giving high marks for adult sex movies like this one! But way I see it this was a good adult spoof!
